        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1178732600">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1178732600" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1178732600" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1178732600">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/kesalin/">飘飘白云</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-04-16</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">单就学术著作可评五星。透过对纲常名教剖析可以看到赤裸裸的吃人真相。中国过去的法，甚至是至现在的法律现实，都是法表儒里-搞有差别化对待，什么刑不上大夫、党内处分，几千年有啥变化？</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1177253539">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1177253539" class="vote-count">0</span>
