          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/23096271/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/23096271/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/55965851/" class=" " title="18622082960">18622082960</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="23096271">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">法是社会产物，法又反映当时社会。探索法的历史，认识法的本质。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-12-11 16:08</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                法是社会产物，法又反映当时社会。探索法的历史，认识法的本质。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







